message.text:
𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

Today, we celebrate not only your special day but also the creativity and dedication you bring as our dear 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐃𝐨𝐜𝐮𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲 𝐒𝐮𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐲𝐚𝐧.

The ITHM Student Council extends our warmest greetings—cheers to you and to another year filled with success, growth, and memorable moments!

May this year open more doors of opportunities, bring endless joy, and inspire you to continue leading with passion and creativity that inspire those around you.

Caption by: Bernadette Gaffud

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

Today, we celebrate not only your special day but also the creativity and dedication you bring as our dear 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐃𝐨𝐜𝐮𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲 𝐒𝐮𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐲𝐚𝐧.

The ITHM Student Council extends our warmest greetings—cheers to you and to another year filled with success, growth, and memorable moments!

May this year open more doors of opportunities, bring endless joy, and inspire you to continue leading with passion and creativity that inspire those around you.

Caption by: Bernadette Gaffud

#CultivatingLimitlessPotential

𝐈𝐭’𝐬 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲’𝐬 𝐃𝐚𝐲 🎉✨

Today, we celebrate not only your special day but also the creativity and dedication you bring as our dear 𝐀𝐬𝐬𝐨𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐃𝐨𝐜𝐮𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐌𝐬. 𝐀𝐬𝐡𝐥𝐞𝐲 𝐒𝐮𝐧𝐠𝐠𝐚𝐲𝐚𝐧.

The ITHM Student Council extends our warmest greetings—cheers to you and to another year filled with success, growth, and memorable moments!

May this year open more doors of opportunities, bring endless joy, and inspire you to continue leading with passion and creativity that inspire those around you.

Caption by: Bernadette Gaffud

message.text:
RE: Independent Learning (only WRP) for September 15-20, 2025

Hello Tams!

I’ve been seeing some students that are confused when it comes to the modality for next week.

Only WRP courses from 3rd to 5th year will be on Independent Study.

Other courses and programs (except those not included from the blended learning modality) will continue the blended setup.

Hoping this clears the confusion for some. For further clarifications, don’t hesitate to send me a DM and the rest of the Executive Board!

Thank you!

- FEU CSO President
